    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>An oolitic limestone widely used for building in England, particularly in London; it is quarried on the Isle of Portland, off the coast of England.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
